data.content:
## What Changed: Microsoft.OpenApi v1 → v2

.NET 10's `Microsoft.AspNetCore.OpenApi` upgraded to **Microsoft.OpenApi v2**, which aligns with OpenAPI 3.1 / JSON Schema. Here are the breaking changes affecting your code:

### 1. `OpenApiString` / `IOpenApiAny` removed
The `Microsoft.OpenApi.Any` namespace is gone. `Schema.Example` is now a `System.Text.Json.Nodes.JsonNode`.

### 2. `Schema.Nullable` removed
OpenAPI 3.1 uses JSON Schema's type-as-flags model. Nullability is expressed by adding `JsonSchemaType.Null` to `Schema.Type`.

### 3. `OpenApiSecurityRequirement` is no longer a dictionary
It's now a simple object with `Scheme` and `Scopes` properties.

---

### Fixed code:

```csharp
using System.Text.Json.Nodes;          // replaces Microsoft.OpenApi.Any
using Microsoft.OpenApi.Models;

options.AddOperationTransformer((operation, context, ct) =>
{
    var param = operation.Parameters.FirstOrDefault(p => p.Name == "api-version");
    if (param is not null)
    {
        // OpenApiString → JsonValue
        param.Schema.Example = JsonValue.Create("1.0");
    }

    operation.Responses.TryAdd("401", new OpenApiResponse { Description = "Unauthorized" });

    var oAuthScheme = new OpenApiSecurityScheme
    {
        Reference = new OpenApiReference { Type = ReferenceType.SecurityScheme, Id = "oauth2" }
    };

    // No longer a Dictionary<scheme, scopes>; each requirement is one scheme + scopes
    operation.Security = new List<OpenApiSecurityRequirement>
    {
        new() { Scheme = oAuthScheme, Scopes = scopes }
    };

    return Task.CompletedTask;
});

options.AddSchemaTransformer((schema, context, ct) =>
{
    if (schema.Properties is not null)
    {
        foreach (var property in schema.Properties)
        {
            if (schema.Required?.Contains(property.Key) != true)
            {
                // Nullable bool is gone; clear the Null flag from the type instead
                property.Value.Type &= ~JsonSchemaType.Null;
            }
        }
    }
    return Task.CompletedTask;
});
```

### Summary of changes

| .NET 9 (OpenApi v1) | .NET 10 (OpenApi v2) |
|---|---|
| `using Microsoft.OpenApi.Any` | `using System.Text.Json.Nodes` |
| `new OpenApiString("1.0")` | `JsonValue.Create("1.0")` |
| `property.Nullable = false` | `property.Type &= ~JsonSchemaType.Null` |
| `new() { [scheme] = scopes }` | `new() { Scheme = scheme, Scopes = scopes }` |
